description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\n Gains resistance against Magic attacks of Ice and Lightning.
description.name: Partial Resistance

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\n Boosts the capacity for all Magic attacks by using additional MP.
description.name: Element Amplification

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nFires ice blocks at multiple enemies. If struck, all monsters other than ice-based ones will freeze. Cannot attack more than 6 at once.
description.name: Ice Strike

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nGathers up the power of lightening and turns it into a spear, attacking a single enemy. Monsters will be damaged with a lightening-based attack.
description.name: Thunder Spear

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nSeals up the enemies around you for a certain amount of time. Once sealed up, the monsters can't use attacking skills, but the skill does not work on boss monsters.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 3 on Element Amplification#
description.name: Seal

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nUses up a significant amount of HP and MP to increase the attacking speed for spells.
description.name: Spell Booster

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nAttacks a single monster with Magic attack of Ice and Lightning features combined.  Very effective to the monsters vulnerable to ice and lightning, and if struck, the monster will freeze.
description.name: Element Composition
